<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٣٩٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5093">أَبُو نُعَيْمٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6092">مِسْعَرٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4505">عَلِيِّ بْنِ الْأَقْمَرِ </a>سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6851">أَبَا جُحَيْفَةَ </a>يَقُولُ: قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«لَا آكُلُ مُتَّكِئًا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>